First Algorithm for Quiz Creation:

1. Import libraries that will be needed.
2. Allow users to choose between the three option (Add category, Access Category, Exit).
3. If users choose add category:
    3.1. Allow users to input the name of category.
    3.2. Create a txt.file using the input.
    3.3. Write in the first line of file the name of category.
4. If users choose Access category:
    4.1 Allow users to choose between the present category.
    4.2 Access the category.
    4.3 Add question, choices, and answer to the category.
    4.4 Ask user if they want to add more.
5. If users choose exit they will be able to exit to the program. 